            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>暴雪娛樂製作的經典 MMORPG《World of Warcraft》（WoW）今年迎接 20 週年之際，提起，就不得不提丹麥著名電競配件製造商 SteelSeries 。過往 SteelSeries 推出了不少電競產品，今次就推出了一系列電競用品慶祝 WoW 20 週年。最近 Unwire 編輯部就收到來自 SteelSeries 的 Arctis Nova 7 Wireless 電競耳機、Aerox 9 Wireless 無線電競滑鼠，以及 QcK 電競滑鼠墊，全部均為 WoW 20 週年紀念款。現在就讓小編和大家開箱看看這幾款精美的電競產品吧。</p><h2>SteelSeries Arctis Nova 7 Wireless 無線電競耳機</h2><p>今次 SteelSeries 推出了兼容性高的 Arctis Nova 7 Wireless，特設 Dongle，不論是 PC、PlayStation、Switch、Mac 的用家都可享受到電競快感，更有快速切換無線耳機功能，只需一鍵即可切換 2.4GHz 或藍牙。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00970-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00970-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00970.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲SteelSeries Arctis Nova 7 Wireless</p><p>打開包裝後，除了耳機本體外，內裏附上了一張 WoW  Grinning Reaver mount 兑換券、一條 USB-C 轉 USB-A 接收器延長線、一條 USB-C 轉 USB-A 線、一條 3.5mm 線，以及一個接收器。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01014-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01014-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01014-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲USB-C 轉 USB-A 接收器延長線、 USB-C 轉 USB-A 線、 3.5mm 線以及接收器</p><h2>上手有份量　耳墊舒適</h2><p>與一般 SteelSeries 的黑色為主不同，SteelSeries Arctis Nova 7 Wireless 這次特地採用了黑金配色，彰顯其 World of Warcraft 20 週年紀念版身份。小編開箱上手後覺得耳機非常扎實，頭帶位置採用金屬材質，其餘如耳筒部分則使用塑膠。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268603" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00974-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00974-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00974.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>頭帶部份可以拆除及移動，耳罩用上了可更換的透氣布網及 AirWeave 記憶棉耳墊，實戴一陣亦不覺侷促，記憶棉耳墊亦非常舒適，不易移位。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00983-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00983-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00983.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可輕鬆徒手拆除頭帶，以便調整至最舒適位置</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00985-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00985-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00985.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳罩厚實，佩戴舒適</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/arctis-nova-5-wireless/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Steelseries Arctis Nova 5 Wireless 耳機　60 小時長續航力 + 一鍵切換 2.4GHz 與藍牙 + 兼容性高</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2><strong>實體按鍵</strong><strong>豐富</strong><strong>　方便玩家快速操作</strong></h2><p>Arctis Nova 7 Wireless 耳罩兩邊均設有不同實體按鍵，讓用家可以在耳機上調節大部份控制。Nova 7 Wireless 左邊設一撥輪用於控制音量，另外亦配備靜音鍵；右邊有開關及藍牙按鍵、ChatMix 控制盤及 USB-C 充電插孔，操作上與大部份 Steelseries 耳機類似。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00978-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00978-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00978.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02052-694x463.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02052-scaled.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲左邊有音量控制撥輪及靜音鍵</picture></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00979-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00979-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00979.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02051-694x463.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02051-scaled.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture>▲右邊有開關及藍牙按鍵、ChatMix 控制盤及 USB-C 充電插孔</picture></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00976-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00976-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00976.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture>▲</picture>伸縮式 ClearCast 咪高峯（開啟）</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00977-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00977-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00977.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02051-694x463.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02051-scaled.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture>▲不使用時可收納回耳罩內</picture></p><h2>Aerox 9 Wireless 無線電競滑鼠</h2><p>SteelSeries Aerox 9 Wireless 左側列出了 12 個數字鍵，可任由玩家自定義，大大增加可塑性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00986-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00986-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00986.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268571" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00993-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00993-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00993.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲內附 USB-C 線、PTFE 滑鼠腳墊、WoW  Lil&#8217; Flameo 兑換券</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00989-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00989-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00989.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲WoW 「W」字標記</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00987-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00987-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00987.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>如果你是 WoW 老玩家，相信會幾欣賞這列快捷鍵，但如果你之前沒有用過同類型滑鼠，要學習用大拇指精準控制這 12 個數字鍵，需要一定時間，因按鍵非常密集且緊湊，要用一定時間熟習慣控制。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00994-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00994-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00994.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲旁邊有 12 個快捷鍵，可由玩家自定義</p><h2>QcK XXL 滑鼠墊（90cm x 40 cm）</h2><p>滑鼠墊上印有改變 Azeroth 歷史的 The Sword of Sargeras，玩家可以用這款 XXL 尺寸的微編織布滑鼠墊裝飾辦公桌。要留意這款滑鼠墊尺寸頗大，長闊為 900 x 400 mm。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268573" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00995-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00995-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00995.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268574" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00997-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00997-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00997.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268575" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01010-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01010-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268576" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01008-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01008-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲滑鼠墊頗大，可容納鍵盤連滑鼠</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/arctis-nova-5-wireless/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Steelseries Arctis Nova 5 Wireless 耳機　60 小時長續航力 + 一鍵切換 2.4GHz 與藍牙 + 兼容性高</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/steelseries-world-of-warcraft/game-channel/">【開箱】SteelSeries x Warcraft 20 週年　Arctis Nova 7 無線耳機 + Aerox 9 無線滑鼠 + QcK 電競滑鼠墊</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
