        </item>
        <item>
            <title>任天堂推智能音樂鬧鐘 Alarmo　可愛遊戲主題可透過動作感應互動</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/nintendo-alarmo/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nintendo-alarmo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/nintendo-alarmo/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:00:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Alarmo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[鬧鐘]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1268382</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>任天堂除了遊戲機之外，間中也會推出一些有趣的週邊商品，最近他們就推出一款智能鬧鐘「Nintendo Sound Clock Alarmo」，除了有經典遊戲角色主題和音效外，鬧鐘功能本身也很實用。<br /><span id="more-1268382"></span></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_11920"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GQimR_GFNgo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Alarmo 的設計簡單，前面設有彩色螢幕（並非觸控螢幕），頂部設有可以着燈的旋鈕和一些按鍵，用家可以選擇自己喜歡的遊戲主題，最初會有「超級瑪利歐奧德賽」、「薩爾達傳説，曠野之息」、「斯普拉遁 3」、「皮克敏 4」和「健身環大冒險」五款遊戲主題可以選擇，除了時間字型變化和畫麪人物會有不同，音效也會是遊戲中的音樂。未來還會免費加入「集合啦！動物森友會」和「瑪利歐賽車 8 豪華版」主題供下載。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fb12f1ed2edd47de1fe7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fb12f1ed2edd47de1fe7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fb12f1ed2edd47de1fe7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268438" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e331a5ae6ea54dab1c40-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e331a5ae6ea54dab1c40-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e331a5ae6ea54dab1c40.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268439" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/edcbc6fe1f3ff8568372-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/edcbc6fe1f3ff8568372-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/edcbc6fe1f3ff8568372.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268440" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/9692b3b3f3b77e2ec2e5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/9692b3b3f3b77e2ec2e5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/9692b3b3f3b77e2ec2e5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e33104d6b7ff1f5c33ed-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e33104d6b7ff1f5c33ed-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e33104d6b7ff1f5c33ed.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>除了基本的鬧鐘功能外，Alarmo 還內置了動作感應器，用家移動身體時會有互動功能，例如，當使用者翻身時會播放金幣音效，離開牀鋪時則會有激勵的聲音，令起牀變成遊戲般的體驗。而如果鬧鐘響起後 20 分鐘內使用者仍未起牀，鬧鐘聲音會變得更加大聲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/shot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/shot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/shot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此外鬧鐘還內置睡眠記錄和睡眠促進音效等其他功能，雖然並不是專業級分析，但仍然有一定的參考價值。而雖然鬧鐘有網絡連線功能，不過並未與手機 App 連動，無法將睡眠數據輸入手機，有點可惜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/alarmo44screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/alarmo44screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/alarmo44screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Alarmo 現於官方網上商店「My Nintendo Store」上向 Nintendo Switch Online 會員限定販售，也會在「Nintendo TOKYO／OSAKA／KYOTO」等官方實體店鋪開始銷售，售價為 12,980 日元，而明年 2 月中開始會在全球發售，有興趣的朋友可以留意了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268442" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/c9664bbc5c6de227a3d0-694x446.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/c9664bbc5c6de227a3d0-694x446.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/c9664bbc5c6de227a3d0.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268443" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/af35d3583e42765776f4-694x446.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/af35d3583e42765776f4-694x446.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/af35d3583e42765776f4.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.nintendo.com/jp/hardware/alarmo/index.html">任天堂</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/15/nintendo-switch-2-rumors/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">任天堂 Switch 2 上市時間，傳最快明年 4 月推出</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/nintendo-switch-official-joy-con-charging-stand/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">任天堂 Switch 上市 7 年半，原廠 Joy-Con 充電座終於推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/nintendo-alarmo/life-tech/">任天堂推智能音樂鬧鐘 Alarmo　可愛遊戲主題可透過動作感應互動</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
